7. User Flow

Citizen registers with phone number → receives OTP → verifies → dashboard.

Submits complaint → complaint stored in DB → status = "Pending."

Panchayat Admin sees complaint → updates status.

Citizen receives real-time update in their dashboard.

Super Admin monitors all operations, generates reports, manages admins.

